    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/26577b179ae314cf66fe54fe8b4aa6bf.poster.avif?t=1772104508\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/26577b179ae314cf66fe54fe8b4aa6bf.webm?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/26577b179ae314cf66fe54fe8b4aa6bf.mp4?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从本地联赛走向世界顶级联赛！带领队伍走上世界之巅！<br>全新经营模拟体验，奋战欧洲顶级联赛。<br><br>从本土走向世界之巅！<br><br>深受玩家喜爱的足球俱乐部经营模拟游戏《创造球会》——系列新作献给全球玩家！<br>世嘉倾情呈现——30年来经久不衰、充满激情与策略的代表性足球游戏！<br><br>《创造球会》由Football Manager ™助力驱动，使用FIFPRO™球员数据，让玩家可在J联赛、K联赛等各大赛事中纵横驰骋！<br><br>化身主教练兼俱乐部经营者，带领球队从本地英雄成长为世界豪门。<br><br>无论身处世界何处，通过跨平台与跨设备联机功能，可随时随地通过移动平台、PC平台以及主机平台免费畅玩本作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/d19e6e9f7a6a4346f66c7aeb9b392080.avif?t=1772104508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras_big/d19e6e9f7a6a4346f66c7aeb9b392080.webp?t=1772104508 width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 真实球员登场</h2>世界真实知名球星于游戏中登场！<br>除了欧洲各大联盟，日本J联盟与韩国K联盟的大量真实选手都收录于游戏中，<br>游戏将有超过5000名以上真实选手任您收集！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/064a61f332c968e6848efb022a6e03aa.poster.avif?t=1772104508\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/064a61f332c968e6848efb022a6e03aa.webm?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/064a61f332c968e6848efb022a6e03aa.mp4?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■作为球会掌旗者的经营体验</h2>作为球会经营者，决定球会未来的经营战略，<br>建设主场，成为前所未有的大球会，<br>在市场中挖角与交易选手，打造完美阵容，<br>并且发掘有潜力的年轻球员，培育成未来的明星选手吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/bfdcdc74d7b7c4d90eaa0baed0acf850.poster.avif?t=1772104508\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/bfdcdc74d7b7c4d90eaa0baed0acf850.webm?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/bfdcdc74d7b7c4d90eaa0baed0acf850.mp4?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■足球传奇的成功之路体验</h2>围绕明星选手打造只属于自己的梦幻队伍，<br>考验你的足球IQ，战术与选手配置，运用智能豪夺胜利！<br>独特选手剧情系统，考验你的领导能力，<br>在这里你能够随心所欲地打造球会，<br>从默默无名开始，踏上挑战之路，挑战世界强权！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/2503a67920ca11ee3fe371c7ef420b1e.poster.avif?t=1772104508\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/2503a67920ca11ee3fe371c7ef420b1e.webm?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271000/extras/2503a67920ca11ee3fe371c7ef420b1e.mp4?t=1772104508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■与监督们展开热烈对战</h2>透过PVP多人游戏模式与其他监督对战，目标是成为世界最强！<br>出战杯赛与国际大赛，赢下光荣胜利，<br>在排行榜上刻下自己的名字，成为永垂不朽的传奇吧！<br><br>#创造球会#SFCC",
